Installation of listeningPort.py is very simple.

Some developers will likely need to install psutils:
    
    pip install psutils

Perhaps you will need to prefix the above pip command with "sudo"
for proper operation.

Read and play with the operating instructions at listeningPort.html .

The copy listeningPort.py to somewhere in your $PATH. A common place 
would be $HOME/bin . 

Rename listeningPort.py to something like listening or listeningPort.

